Interface ICMToken

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IASToken, IMXMLToken
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface ICMToken
    Range that represents a generic token within code model

      • changeType

        ICMToken changeType(int type)
        Changes the type of the token, and returns a new copy with the desired type. This is non-destructive
        Parameters:
        type - the type of token to create
        Returns:
        a new ICMToken that is a copy of the original, with a different type

      • getSourcePath

        String getSourcePath()
        Get the source file path of the node. When the token is built from an included source, this method returns the file path of the included source. The return value can be null if the source file is not an included file, but not every non-included file has a null source path.

        The source path will be copied to ISourceLocation.getSourcePath() during tree construction.

        Returns:
        source file path or null
